<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Syakira Reynamahira | Portfolio</title>

  <!--
    REYNA'S LUXURY PORTFOLIO WEBSITE

    IMAGE GUIDE:
    Put your images in the same folder as this file.
    Use these names:
    profile.jpg
    achievement-1.jpg
    achievement-2.jpg
    ...
    achievement-17.jpg
  -->

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --black: #070508;
      --deep-plum: #130817;
      --royal-plum: #2a102d;
      --ruby: #8f1d45;
      --rose: #e7a6b8;
      --blush: #ffd7df;
      --gold: #f3d78b;
      --pale-gold: #fff1bc;
      --emerald: #5fc7a5;
      --sapphire: #6ea8ff;
      --cream: #fff8ee;
      --muted: rgba(255, 248, 238, 0.72);
      --soft: rgba(255, 248, 238, 0.45);
      --border: rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.24);
      --card: rgba(255, 248, 238, 0.075);
      --card-strong: rgba(255, 248, 238, 0.12);
      --shadow: 0 34px 100px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
      --serif: "Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif;
      --sans: "Inter", sans-serif;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: var(--sans);
      color: var(--cream);
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 8%, rgba(143, 29, 69, 0.48), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 10%, rgba(95, 199, 165, 0.17), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 75% 48%, rgba(110, 168, 255, 0.12), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 100%, rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.16), transparent 38%),
        linear-gradient(145deg, var(--black), var(--deep-plum) 48%, #050305);
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 62px 62px;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 35%, transparent 82%);
      z-index: -2;
    }

    body::after {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.035), transparent 18%, transparent 82%, rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.035)),
        radial-gradient(circle at center, transparent 45%, rgba(0,0,0,0.32));
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(1160px, calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: auto;
    }

    .lux-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 248, 238, 0.11), rgba(255, 248, 238, 0.035)),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.05), rgba(231, 166, 184, 0.035));
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 9px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--pale-gold);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      box-shadow: 0 0 35px rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.17);
    }

    .sparkle {
      color: var(--gold);
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.8));
    }

    nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 999;
      padding: 16px 0;
      background: rgba(7, 5, 8, 0.72);
      backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.15);
    }

    .nav-inner {
      width: min(1160px, calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--pale-gold);
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 29px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .logo-mark {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 50%;
      color: #16070d;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 35% 25%, #fff8d8, transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pale-gold), var(--gold), var(--rose), var(--ruby));
      box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.38);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      list-style: none;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 6px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.17);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.045);
    }

    .nav-links a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      border-radius: 999px;
      transition: 0.25s ease;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover,
    .nav-links a.active {
      color: #17080f;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pale-gold), var(--gold), var(--rose));
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.24);
    }

    .menu-toggle {
      display: none;
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      color: var(--cream);
      font-size: 22px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: 88vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 64px;
      padding: 94px 0 74px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: "PORTFOLIO";
      position: absolute;
      top: 8%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: clamp(80px, 15vw, 215px);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: rgba(255, 248, 238, 0.035);
      pointer-events: none;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: clamp(64px, 8vw, 122px);
      line-height: 0.88;
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
    }

    .hero h1 span {
      display: block;
      background: linear-gradient(110deg, var(--cream), var(--pale-gold), var(--rose), var(--gold));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 24px rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.13));
    }

    .subtitle {
      margin-top: 24px;
      color: var(--pale-gold);
      font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 23px);
      font-weight: 600;
      max-width: 670px;
    }

    .hero-description {
      margin-top: 16px;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 670px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .hero-note {
      margin-top: 30px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .note-pill {
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.18);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
      color: var(--pale-gold);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .profile-stage {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 560px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
    }

    .profile-frame {
      position: relative;
      width: min(410px, 86vw);
      aspect-ratio: 0.78;
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 48% 48% 34px 34px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.32);
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 241, 188, 0.24), rgba(231, 166, 184, 0.09)),
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow), 0 0 80px rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.13);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .profile-frame::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 241, 188, 0.26);
      border-radius: 48% 48% 24px 24px;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .profile-photo {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 46% 46% 24px 24px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 35% 20%, rgba(255, 241, 188, 0.38), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(143, 29, 69, 0.72), rgba(42, 16, 45, 0.94));
      display: block;
    }

    .profile-label {
      position: absolute;
      left: 34px;
      right: 34px;
      bottom: 34px;
      z-index: 4;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.24);
      background: rgba(7, 5, 8, 0.52);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }

    .profile-label h3 {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 32px;
      line-height: 1;
      color: var(--pale-gold);
    }

    .profile-label p {
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .floating-gem {
      position: absolute;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.25);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.075);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      animation: float 5.5s ease-in-out infinite;
      z-index: 5;
    }

    .gem-1 {
      width: 94px;
      height: 94px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      top: 40px;
      right: 8px;
      font-size: 34px;
    }

    .gem-2 {
      width: 78px;
      height: 78px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      left: 8px;
      bottom: 118px;
      font-size: 30px;
      animation-delay: -1.4s;
    }

    .gem-3 {
      width: 122px;
      height: 54px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      right: -6px;
      bottom: 46px;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      animation-delay: -2.4s;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translateY(-18px) rotate(3deg);
      }
    }

    section:not(.hero) {
      padding: 90px 0;
    }

    .section-heading {
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 38px;
    }

    .section-title h2,
    .contact-content h2 {
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: clamp(46px, 5vw, 76px);
      line-height: 0.96;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .section-title p,
    .contact-content p {
      margin-top: 16px;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    .divider-line {
      height: 1px;
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 140px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.36));
    }

    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .about-main {
      padding: 34px;
      border-radius: 34px;
    }

    .about-main p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .about-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.15);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat .number {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 39px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--gold);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .stat .label {
      margin-top: 7px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .signature {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 35px;
      color: var(--pale-gold);
    }

    .about-side {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .mini-card {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 24px;
    }

    .mini-card h3,
    .skill-category h3 {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 31px;
      color: var(--pale-gold);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .mini-card p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .achievements-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .achievement-card {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 34px;
      transition: 0.35s ease;
    }

    .achievement-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      border-color: rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.5);
      box-shadow: 0 38px 110px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.58), 0 0 50px rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.14);
    }

    .achievement-content {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .achievement-kicker {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .achievement-content h3 {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1.05;
      color: var(--pale-gold);
    }

    .achievement-result {
      color: var(--rose);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-top: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .achievement-content p {
      margin-top: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .achievement-tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 9px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .tag,
    .skill-item {
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.18);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
      color: var(--pale-gold);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .tag {
      padding: 6px 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .skills-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .skill-category {
      padding: 26px;
      border-radius: 34px;
    }

    .skill-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .skill-item {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 7px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: 0.25s ease;
    }

    .skill-item::before {
      content: "✦";
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .skill-item:hover {
      color: var(--cream);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      background: rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.09);
    }

    .contact-panel {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 36px;
      border-radius: 34px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 32px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .contact-panel::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 12% 20%, rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.22), transparent 26%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 70%, rgba(143, 29, 69, 0.34), transparent 34%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .contact-content,
    .contact-details {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .contact-details {
      display: grid;
      gap: 13px;
    }

    .contact-item {
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(243, 215, 139, 0.18);
      background: rgba(7, 5, 8, 0.36);
    }

    .contact-item .label {
      display: block;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .contact-item .value {
      color: var(--cream);
      font-weight: 700;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 34px 0 48px;
      color: var(--soft);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero,
      .about-grid,
      .contact-panel {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero {
        min-height: auto;
        padding-top: 72px;
      }

      .profile-stage {
        min-height: 500px;
      }

      .achievements-grid,
      .skills-container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .container,
      .nav-inner {
        width: min(100% - 30px, 1160px);
      }

      .menu-toggle {
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
      }

      .nav-links {
        position: absolute;
        top: calc(100% + 12px);
        left: 15px;
        right: 15px;
        display: none;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
        padding: 12px;
        border-radius: 24px;
        background: rgba(13, 8, 14, 0.96);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .nav-links.active {
        display: flex;
      }

      .nav-links a {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .section-heading {
        display: block;
      }

      .divider-line {
        margin-top: 22px;
      }

      .achievements-grid,
      .skills-container,
      .about-stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .profile-stage {
        min-height: 410px;
      }

      .profile-frame {
        width: min(335px, 92vw);
      }

      .gem-1 {
        right: -4px;
      }

      .gem-2 {
        left: -4px;
      }

      .contact-panel,
      .about-main {
        padding: 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="#home" class="logo">
        <span class="logo-mark">◆</span>
        <span>Syakira Reynamahira</span>
      </a>

      <button class="menu-toggle" onclick="toggleMenu()">☰</button>

      <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
        <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="#achievements">Achievements</a></li>
        <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <header class="hero container" id="home">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <span class="eyebrow"><span class="sparkle">✦</span> A little sparkle, a lot of ambition</span>

        <h1>
          Hi, I’m
          <span>Syakira Reynamahira</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="subtitle">
          Student • Research Enthusiast • MUN Delegate • Creative Achiever
        </p>

        <p class="hero-description">
        Through this portfolio, I want to share the achievements, competitions, and experiences that have shaped my journey.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-note">
          <span class="note-pill">Model United Nations</span>
          <span class="note-pill">Research & Innovation</span>
          <span class="note-pill">Science & Mathematics</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="profile-stage">
        <div class="floating-gem gem-1">⊛</div>
        <div class="floating-gem gem-2">✧</div>
        <div class="floating-gem gem-3">Portfolio</div>

        <div class="profile-frame">
          <img src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1tWH1IdJGpwtXD140MVlz46EEFx7u-dam&sz=w1000" alt="Syakira Reynamahira profile photo" class="profile-photo">
          <div class="profile-label">
            <h3>Reyna</h3>
            <p>Chasing dreams with grace, grit, and a little glitter.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <div class="section-title">
            <span class="eyebrow"><span class="sparkle">✦</span> About Me</span>
            <h2>The Story Behind My Sparkle</h2>
            <p>A glimpse into who I am, what I love, and the journey I am building one challenge at a time.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="divider-line"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-grid">
          <div class="about-main lux-card">
            <p>Hi, I am Syakira Reynamahira, but you can call me Reyna. I am 15 years old and I am a curious, ambitious student who loves learning through competitions, research, and creative projects.</p>
            <p>My journey is shaped by different experiences, from Model United Nations and science olympiads to research competitions, mathematics, innovation, and international opportunities. I enjoy challenging myself in many fields because every competition teaches me something new.</p>
            <p>This portfolio is a collection of my achievements, growth, and dreams. It represents my dedication to keep learning, improving, and turning every challenge into something meaningful, memorable, and golden.</p>

            <div class="about-stats">
              <div class="stat">
                <div class="number" id="achievementCount">17</div>
                <div class="label">Achievements</div>
              </div>

              <div class="stat">
                <div class="number">10</div>
                <div class="label">Years Learning</div>
              </div>

              <div class="stat">
                <div class="number">∞</div>
                <div class="label">Curiosity</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="signature">Syakira Reynamahira</div>
          </div>

          <div class="about-side">
